{"word":"G3453 - μυέω - myéō - moo-eh'-o - Instruct","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μυέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">myéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">moo-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Instruct</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போதிக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to initiate into the mysteries"},{"paragraph":"2. to teach fully, instruct; to accustom one to a thing to give one an intimate acquaintance with a thing"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G3466 - μυστήριον - mystḗrion - moos-tay'-ree-on/3466\">G3466</a>; to <i>initiate</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>teach:</i> - instruct.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3453/3453\">G3453</a>, <a href=\"#/G3466/3466\">G3466</a>"}]}